                                                        <p>As an inaugural initiative of our student chapter, we are excited to announce our first step to our go green initiative <strong>'PLANT THE FUTURE'</strong>. Aiming to create awareness from the grassroot level. We believe this small step can create a major impact on our growing community at <strong>ARCITE</strong> .</p>
                                                    <p>All future students of <strong> ARCITE</strong> will be awarded with a plant as a symbol of sustainable development. This would sow the seed to a new generation of professionals who imparts the importance of sustainable development and eco friendly built environment.</p>
